{"tid":2518090,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"羅力威算唔算生不逢時先搞到依家咁半紅不黑?","createTime":"2021-05-05T20:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T20:35:32.000Z","uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"866ad0637000a2980930f50d9fbc95be0cfb36de","tid":2518090,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:27:34.000Z","msg":"如果佢早10-1x年出道:<br />\n1) atv 仲係全盛, 好多藝人之後仲有得爆紅, 例如張家輝, 江華; 但羅力威已經係atv末期, atv 又唔夠力捧, 佢又救唔到atv, 累鬥累, 之後轉去英皇已經過左最hit時期<br />\n2) 佢咁中意作普通話歌, 97年, 08年作返首中囯人的驕傲, 今日紅過劉德華<br />\n3) 佢咁中意扮周杰倫, 2000年前先出道, 就係周杰倫扮佢<br />\n<br />\n如果佢遲10-1x年出道:<br />\n1) 上去支那唔敢講紅過gem, 但起碼值得紅過陳偉霆先<br />\n2) 參加全民造星, 是撚但都紅la 有連登仔撐, 做乜都係黃<br />\n3) 扮得似周杰倫都係才華, 中国人最中意, 你睇鄧超接廣告/配音接到手軟, 黃祖藍扮女人都身家過億, 羅力威扮周杰倫做小丑起碼身家十億; 起碼唔洗比d 咩吳國敬肥媽屌鳩你唔好再扮周杰倫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Jy62QtiF0xE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJy62QtiF0xE&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=3abe03a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Jy62QtiF0xE</a>"},{"pid":"28ff7b3028ac4c8fe813a435aa6e060e1e0dea32","tid":2518090,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:29:14.000Z","msg":"佢屌到雨橋已經人生打爆機"},{"pid":"1b5a2ac22fe278dc9675ba3ff333505d4caf2939","tid":2518090,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:29:44.000Z","msg":"Who?"},{"pid":"7f044f3eea16e31619f4d005f70cb1856559ace3","tid":2518090,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28ff7b3028ac4c8fe813a435aa6e060e1e0dea32","tid":2518090,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:29:14.000Z","msg":"佢屌到雨橋已經人生打爆機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:31:02.000Z","msg":"佢早d 出世屌到阿嬌, stephy<br />\n遲d 出世有牙冰 jessica"},{"pid":"5eb18cd0c688eb1bf281ab139adfdc3789880a74","tid":2518090,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b5a2ac22fe278dc9675ba3ff333505d4caf2939","tid":2518090,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":1